1
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:33,320
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,350 --> 00:00:36,340
[Episode 20
A Misplaced Heart, Hard to Restore]

3
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,150
Boss Qian,

4
00:00:46,170 --> 00:00:47,730
please wait a moment.

5
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:48,820
Thank you.

6
00:01:21,170 --> 00:01:22,060
Magistrate,

7
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:23,650
why is it you?

8
00:01:24,289 --> 00:01:24,780
You...

9
00:01:26,140 --> 00:01:27,400
Have a seat, Boss Qian.

10
00:01:28,140 --> 00:01:30,340
Whatever it is, let's sit down and talk.

11
00:01:30,890 --> 00:01:32,810
My men are all outside.

12
00:01:34,090 --> 00:01:35,420
If this gets out of hand,

13
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:37,140
it won't end well

14
00:01:37,530 --> 00:01:38,620
for you.

15
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,820
I know what he wants.

16
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:55,560
Speaking of which,

17
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:56,860
this body of mine

18
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:58,810
was his first choice,

19
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,550
and the best fit.

20
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:02,260
I came here this time,

21
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:03,580
hoping that

22
00:02:04,290 --> 00:02:06,420
everything returns to where it began.

23
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:08,850
Then,

24
00:02:09,130 --> 00:02:10,460
what do you mean by that?

25
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:16,970
My time is short.

26
00:02:18,130 --> 00:02:19,180
All I want is

27
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,910
peace for Yin-Yang Crossing

28
00:02:21,250 --> 00:02:22,710
and safety for its people.

29
00:02:23,970 --> 00:02:26,500
I will trade this body
he's always dreamed of,

30
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,160
to end the war,

31
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:32,079
and bring back the people he abducted.

32
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,920
If I fulfill his lifelong wish,

33
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:40,690
perhaps,

34
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:41,900
it'llplease him,

35
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,060
and your Jinlang

36
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:44,940
will come back unharmed.

37
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:31,050
[Gilded Grotto]

38
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,350
The people are innocent.

39
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,930
How could you kill them all?

40
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:19,050
A little nourishment,
but better than nothing.

41
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:20,940
To be devoured by me

42
00:05:21,370 --> 00:05:23,330
is a worthy end for them.

43
00:05:24,330 --> 00:05:25,330
Take a good look

44
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,210
at yourself.

45
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:29,680
Now that you have lost the tree heart,

46
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,770
to me,

47
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:33,840
you're nothing but a well-crafted vessel.

48
00:05:34,610 --> 00:05:36,940
No different from those ants.

49
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:39,280
I don't want it that much anymore.

50
00:05:39,990 --> 00:05:40,909
Guess

51
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:43,340
why I am still willing to see you

52
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:47,580
and agree to your ridiculous deal?

53
00:05:48,659 --> 00:05:50,570
Because I mean something

54
00:05:50,890 --> 00:05:52,210
to Liu Fufeng.

55
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:55,540
Once you possess my body,

56
00:05:55,810 --> 00:05:58,180
the next time you face her,

57
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,270
she will hesitate.

58
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:02,200
And this moment of hesitation

59
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:04,420
will be your chance of survival.

60
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:07,210
You're half right.

61
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:08,510
Young Magistrate.

62
00:06:08,970 --> 00:06:10,210
The other half is

63
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:11,970
I want to see for myself

64
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,610
what tricks you can play

65
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:16,060
with your dying body.

66
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:17,010
No tricks.

67
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:18,860
I came this time

68
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:21,250
for the peace of Yin-Yang Crossing.

69
00:06:21,660 --> 00:06:23,210
She's also willing to make a concession

70
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:24,270
to grant your wish,

71
00:06:24,810 --> 00:06:27,570
sacrificing me alone for a time of peace.

72
00:06:29,820 --> 00:06:30,790
She has finally

73
00:06:32,050 --> 00:06:33,500
learned to compromise.

74
00:06:49,530 --> 00:06:50,409
Wait for me.

75
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:29,250
As expected,

76
00:08:30,810 --> 00:08:33,780
this body is the most comfortable.

77
00:08:35,940 --> 00:08:36,809
Qian Wanqian,

78
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:40,450
you did well this time.

79
00:08:44,970 --> 00:08:45,900
No need.

80
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:49,780
This body has long been hollowed out
by evil power.

81
00:08:49,940 --> 00:08:50,780
Leave it to me

82
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:52,180
as nourishment.

83
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:07,220
Spirit-Trapping Spell.

84
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:08,020
A gift for you.

85
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,040
Hurry. Purge...

86
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:13,550
Purge the evil power.

87
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:14,850
Keep purging it.

88
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:15,810
Quick!

89
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:19,200
You... You... You!

90
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:20,570
What are you doing?

91
00:09:20,570 --> 00:09:21,570
Stop her quickly!

92
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:23,760
Fengling,

93
00:09:23,890 --> 00:09:24,560
I'll protect you.

94
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:25,290
Go quickly!

95
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:27,440
Qian Wanqian,

96
00:09:27,970 --> 00:09:28,940
open your eyes!

97
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:30,270
See how many lives he has taken.

98
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:32,000
Now he wants to devour your son.

99
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:33,660
To him, you and your son

100
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,570
are nothing but disposable vessels.

101
00:09:35,570 --> 00:09:38,770
Do you want to watch
Jinlang's soul be destroyed forever?

102
00:09:40,090 --> 00:09:40,540
Purge!

103
00:09:41,090 --> 00:09:42,260
Let her purge it quickly!

104
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:43,190
Let her purge it!

105
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:52,690
Trying to trap me?

106
00:09:57,690 --> 00:09:58,850
Jinlang, hurry,

107
00:09:59,380 --> 00:10:01,020
come with me.

108
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,660
Hurry. Let's go.

109
00:10:02,990 --> 00:10:03,510
Hurry.

110
00:10:20,090 --> 00:10:20,690
Remember,

111
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:23,370
when the Spirit-Trapping Spell
takes effect,

112
00:10:23,370 --> 00:10:25,280
it will temporarily trap
Bai Han's spiritual consciousness

113
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:27,160
within your body.

114
00:10:28,490 --> 00:10:30,400
Your only way out

115
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:31,810
is to rely on your sheer willpower

116
00:10:31,810 --> 00:10:33,610
to walk out of the Gilded Grotto,

117
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:35,770
and step into the formation I have set.

118
00:10:36,830 --> 00:10:38,070
Only then

119
00:10:38,570 --> 00:10:40,040
can we destroy him

120
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:41,880
once and for all.

121
00:12:11,540 --> 00:12:12,090
Fufeng,

122
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:13,550
it's me.

123
00:12:17,810 --> 00:12:18,780
Your imitation

124
00:12:19,420 --> 00:12:20,480
is not convincing.

125
00:12:21,690 --> 00:12:23,820
Are you going to watch us die together?

126
00:13:19,970 --> 00:13:21,180
His mortal body

127
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:25,210
cannot withstand the life-force backlash
from the spiritual pool.

128
00:13:25,210 --> 00:13:26,970
His main meridians are severed,

129
00:13:26,970 --> 00:13:28,230
and his soul is fading.

130
00:13:29,170 --> 00:13:31,390
The spiritual pool can at best
preserve his flesh

131
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,960
until 9 AM tomorrow.

132
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,850
Then isn't there any other way?

133
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:37,780
Don't you have

134
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,880
plenty of reishi mushrooms
and celestial herbs at Xiqianhua?

135
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:40,810
Or ginseng?

136
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:42,050
Even thousand-year-old ginseng would do.

137
00:13:42,050 --> 00:13:42,860
I'll get it.

138
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:44,150
I'd brave mountains of blades
and seas of fire to get it.

139
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:46,350
What's the use of you risking your life?

140
00:13:49,810 --> 00:13:50,610
Xiaohu,

141
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:52,860
you must understand.

142
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:56,780
He is not a spirit or monster.

143
00:13:57,090 --> 00:13:58,520
He has no spiritual consciousness
to gather,

144
00:13:58,520 --> 00:14:00,050
nor a demon core to nourish.

145
00:14:01,540 --> 00:14:02,850
His mortal days are over,

146
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:04,850
and his soul returns to the underworld.

147
00:14:04,850 --> 00:14:06,710
Xiqianhua is not the Hall of Yama.

148
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,710
We cannot rewrite
the Book of Life and Death.

149
00:14:13,090 --> 00:14:14,300
What about Lady Fufeng?

150
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:15,490
She is a thousand-year demon.

151
00:14:15,490 --> 00:14:17,090
She must have a way, right?

152
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:24,700
Master has done everything she could.

153
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:34,360
I don't believe it.

154
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:36,900
Lord Bai won't...

155
00:14:37,330 --> 00:14:38,380
He won't...

156
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:40,190
He won't just...

157
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:48,540
Xiqianhua will follow proper rites

158
00:14:48,890 --> 00:14:51,550
to bathe him, dress him,
and prepare his coffin.

159
00:14:51,970 --> 00:14:53,030
Since you are here,

160
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:55,910
please relay this
to Deputy Magistrate Shi:

161
00:14:55,970 --> 00:14:58,370
in keeping with the rites
for a fallen imperial official,

162
00:14:58,370 --> 00:15:02,020
detail Lord Bai's achievements
and the circumstances of his death.

163
00:15:02,020 --> 00:15:03,080
As for the funeral,

164
00:15:04,850 --> 00:15:06,310
Xiqianhua will handle it.

165
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:09,680
This is

166
00:15:10,810 --> 00:15:11,850
how it ends.

167
00:15:25,210 --> 00:15:26,180
You said

168
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:30,410
people should do what they want to do.

169
00:15:32,180 --> 00:15:33,840
All I want is to be a constable.

170
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,660
Now that you're gone,

171
00:15:36,660 --> 00:15:38,060
where am I supposed to go?

172
00:16:14,540 --> 00:16:15,940
Master, don't go to look.

173
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:19,330
Your heart will soften again.

174
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,700
And if it does,

175
00:16:21,850 --> 00:16:24,110
will you give him that half-heart again?

176
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:30,060
Now this half-heart has been nourished
by spiritual power.

177
00:16:30,330 --> 00:16:31,500
It has revived.

178
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:34,030
If you give it to Lord Bai,

179
00:16:34,090 --> 00:16:35,060
it would be like letting him

180
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:36,460
share half of your power.

181
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,910
Power corrupts the heart.

182
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:41,690
Eternal life warps desire.

183
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:44,260
Bai Han is proof of that.

184
00:16:45,570 --> 00:16:47,090
If you give him this heart

185
00:16:47,090 --> 00:16:48,380
at all costs today,

186
00:16:48,970 --> 00:16:50,970
ten or a hundred years from now,

187
00:16:51,450 --> 00:16:53,180
will he become the next Bai Han?

188
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:55,040
Will he become the next

189
00:16:55,610 --> 00:16:57,740
source of chaos in Yin-Yang Crossing?

190
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:01,210
Besides,

191
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:04,310
the method of reversing life
is extremely perilous.

192
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:05,990
If you separate the tree heart again

193
00:17:05,990 --> 00:17:07,720
to infuse it into a mortal body,

194
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,530
his mortal body

195
00:17:09,530 --> 00:17:11,390
likely could not bear that power,

196
00:17:11,930 --> 00:17:14,630
and in the end,
he might scatter to nothing.

197
00:17:15,339 --> 00:17:16,140
Master, you may suffer

198
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:19,069
the backlash of having your heart
torn out once more.

199
00:17:20,770 --> 00:17:22,250
Now that this half-heart

200
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:24,359
has finally returned to you.

201
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:28,030
It cannot endure another separation.

202
00:18:01,120 --> 00:18:02,650
Since there is no next life,

203
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:05,110
may you forget this old friend soon.

204
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,400
May spring fill all your days ahead.

205
00:18:10,970 --> 00:18:11,820
Lady Fufeng.

206
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:14,620
I will go find Bai Han tomorrow.

207
00:18:15,730 --> 00:18:17,730
I brought wine from Zuiwang Tavern.

208
00:18:17,890 --> 00:18:20,300
Fengling said it's your favorite.

209
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:22,420
Let's have a drink together,

210
00:18:22,420 --> 00:18:23,070
shall we?

211
00:18:28,690 --> 00:18:29,180
My Lady.

212
00:18:30,940 --> 00:18:33,010
I thought the day I returned the heart

213
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:34,290
would be my final day.

214
00:18:35,210 --> 00:18:36,300
I didn't expect

215
00:18:36,330 --> 00:18:38,130
to be granted a little more time.

216
00:18:39,490 --> 00:18:41,720
Today, let's set aside official business,

217
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,050
just drink and be merry,

218
00:18:43,210 --> 00:18:44,050
shall we?

219
00:18:45,810 --> 00:18:46,430
Okay.

220
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:01,900
The willow leaf jade pendant you gave me,

221
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:04,100
does it have spiritual consciousness?

222
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:08,140
It's too young.

223
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,590
It has yet to awaken.

224
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,010
Is that so?

225
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:15,350
Then if there is a next life,

226
00:19:16,330 --> 00:19:18,130
I will become that jade pendant,

227
00:19:18,180 --> 00:19:19,690
just like the Ring Spirit.

228
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:21,940
Once I gain spiritual consciousness,

229
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:23,140
I will take human form

230
00:19:24,050 --> 00:19:25,690
and stay by your side

231
00:19:26,050 --> 00:19:27,650
as your most capable helper.

232
00:19:28,050 --> 00:19:28,910
How about that?

233
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:41,180
The light fades with one's passing.

234
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:44,510
What talk is there of reincarnation?

235
00:19:48,530 --> 00:19:51,090
Lady Fufeng, you truly are no fun.

236
00:19:52,970 --> 00:19:53,820
I know

237
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:56,290
our paths crossed too briefly,

238
00:19:57,850 --> 00:19:59,150
but I never got a chance

239
00:19:59,490 --> 00:20:00,770
to look my fill of you.

240
00:20:06,370 --> 00:20:07,410
What a pity.

241
00:20:19,850 --> 00:20:20,400
Here.

242
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,680
Since that's the case,

243
00:20:31,450 --> 00:20:32,840
I wish Lady Fufeng

244
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:34,850
all the best.

245
00:22:05,770 --> 00:22:06,620
I know

246
00:22:08,050 --> 00:22:09,780
you are different from Bai Han.

247
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:11,490
Bai Shanjun,

248
00:22:14,210 --> 00:22:15,450
don't let me down.

249
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:22,380
If you think our time together
was too brief,

250
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,080
then live on.

251
00:23:25,390 --> 00:23:27,120
If you prove yourself useless,

252
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:29,280
I will do as you said:

253
00:23:30,570 --> 00:23:32,170
forget this old friend soon,

254
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,200
and let all days ahead be spring.

